summary: A Retexture of Azuras Star to make it look.. mh - better?
descriptionHtml:
Ingame the quest with Azuras Star got three different kinds of it

1) the broken one
2) bring it back to the shrine: Azuras Star
3) bring it to Winterhold: The black Star

This is a retexture of all of them - because the Vanilla ones look.. kind of unrealistic

You like it? Then take a look at one of my other mods: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4380
author: Harodath
